Package: gAtom
Type: Package
Title: Graph Atom Decomposition for igraph Objects
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Heng", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "peiheng@nenu.edu.cn")
Description: Provides graph atom decomposition utilities backed by a C implementation
    using igraph C APIs. The package exposes two interfaces for computing
    a minimal collapsible set and decomposing a graph into atoms and separators.
